      "widgets_values": [
        "A moody portrait of a mad K-pop idol in a decayed renaissance dress of faded pink lace, eyes are blind folded with black cloth, curly silver long hair, stained and worn, layered with black corset bindings. Around her neck blooms a collar of dark roses and rotten rats, with a red-black rose heart some fresh, some rotting, some red splatter on her costume and her face. Her expression is soft but eerie, eyes slightly unfocused. Skin has subtle imperfections, like faint bruising or age cracks. Background is a desolate garden overtaken by dead vines and fog. Lighting is muted, gray-green tones with soft diffusion. Style is melancholic, painterly, with gothic decay"
